Zero point energy                ...      0.33815034 Eh     212.19 kcal/mol
Thermal vibrational correction   ...      0.02448141 Eh      15.36 kcal/mol
Thermal rotational correction    ...      0.00141627 Eh       0.89 kcal/mol
